fr.sorbonne_u.components.pubsub.components

Class Publisher

  • java.lang.Object
    • fr.sorbonne_u.components.AbstractComponent
      • fr.sorbonne_u.components.pubsub.components.Publisher
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    fr.sorbonne_u.components.ComponentI, PublisherService

    public class Publisher
extends fr.sorbonne_u.components.AbstractComponent
implements PublisherService
    A Publisher component handles publishing messages to the PubSub. The Publisher implement all the methods of the PublisherService interface methods and delegates their implementations to its PublisherOutBoundPort. This component has only one required interface: PublisherService.Required

    In a CVM, this component need to establish the connection between his out-bound port and a PubSub component, however, in a Distributed CVM, this component need to establish the connection between his out-bound port and a PubSubNode component in-bound port.

    See Also:
    PublisherService, PublisherOutBoundPort, PublisherServiceConnector
